<description>
<![CDATA[ 
	<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">一个人只要不是专业的哲学研究者，绝不主张去阅读晦涩难懂的哲学原著，如果一开始就硬着头皮咬着牙去肯像</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61+X3LfLfS1FWimuuq+5CF40jC6oCtSBY/WbalqUVRcJqVuz7qzNqYct6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">《纯粹理性批判》</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">《精神现象学》这类书籍 这只会在你阅读经验中烙下伤心惨目的印记，而那对于初接触哲学的爱好者，究竟读那种书好，这是各花入各眼的问题，可以集思广益的展开讨论，我觉着一个人的个性喜好如何，往往会决定他选择阅读的书的档次和质量。在这一点上，例如别人推崇的</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61+X3LfLfS1FYQTG7utUfeMO8CTZNveOO+ydcWAB03uJCJjrlJfaGyHXrFKr4XEc/oV0rsM/W/ehK2oFpmdY3q9V0LsaDl4ULHFfCgj4klPBgn2NG94ByuYpE984sAve4w2VKhg7h1+qVUL/AVHxmT+zVlUfr4Ft9pBYZ+UlBZ0WF3UdcT1QiKVdj2oeHoEzTI=" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">《苏菲的世界》</a><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw61+X3LfLfS1FT5aRNMpaOdpsYHDtHjZ0Y8iY65SX2hsh16xSq+FxHP6FdK7DP1v3oStqBaZnWN6vVdC7Gg5eFCxxXwoI+JJTwYJ9jRveAcrmKRPfOLAL3uMNlSoYO4dfqlVC/wFR8Zk/s1ZVH6+BbfaQWGflJQWdFhd1HXE9UIilXY9qHh6BM0y" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">《小王子》</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">《通俗哲学教材》等等...这些虽然不是烂书，但都对不上我的口味，现我特别推荐下自己阅读过的一些经典入门书籍：</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">我喜欢把哲学史类的书籍定位为哲学入门书籍，所有的《</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60Vu3AoSLgrRN/6cP9cxCUCNu5AOtWml363pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrI8pbaiVjsTaVac5zdSSrIf5CPB8ohaihq4Zzuj7vhkMHh5d4ADz2oEw1pzeVCBaOexK80u/B26+VWZhAVR4xoKDA8Zu4mdgY0" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">西方哲学</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">史》类书籍中，这是我看过最好的一本，历史上所有伟大哲学家的主要观点，生平和影响，都被作者用鲜活详实的语言，完整的记录下来了，为了让这书更好的传播，作者在写作此书的时候就一直在避免用枯燥的哲学专业术语，和学院式腔调，这使得整本书在讲述哲学家和他们的问题时，既深入浅出，但又不落俗套。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=14275d8e2f2eb938ec6d7afae56385fe/ee0735fae6cd7b89de9164ec0f2442a7d8330edb.jpg" border="0" width="200" height="290" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">提到</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw628daWx2ha6G34qXiTmj2bqImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">叔本华</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">多数人最推崇他的《为意志和表象的世界》在哲学原著类书籍中相比</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63qqEcm50YDP/ShDIEZN6fVt6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">康德</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">等人，这本书更加容易让人着迷，不过另的这本《叔本华论说文集》观点更加另类，精辟，文笔也更加优美，叔本华对于世界，人生的所有思考都清晰的展现在这本书里了。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=b998a7e06c81800a6ee58906813433d6/891bb051f81986185ebab1eb4aed2e738ad4e6e4.jpg" border="0" width="300" height="441" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">这本书和第一本差不多，但是有些哲学观点，例如20世纪的分析哲学，存在主义，此书补充的更详尽，也更通俗。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=147421b22e738bd4c421b239918a876c/88b7d0a20cf431ad052f1d564b36acaf2fdd98e4.jpg" border="0" width="416" height="568" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">我觉得这是了解哲学为何物时绝不能跳过的一本书，有些作家很有学问，但是他不屑于做普及哲学的工作，他认为这样会很掉价，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63TFLATSO+KmsWKFh8ZUA0KImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">周国平</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">不一样，他是一直致力于用平易近人的文风来讲述古奥精深的哲学问题。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=f6ded5566b63f6241c5d390bb745eb32/eb09b3de9c82d158c87e07de800a19d8bd3e42e4.jpg" border="0" width="306" height="435" /><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">这本书和</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63TFLATSO+KmsWKFh8ZUA0KImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">周国平</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">的差不多，不过更为专业，每个提到的陌生人名，地名，书籍都有详尽的注释，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62oj1ncRVdR/TFnbEQR5H4zImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">何兆武</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">曾经翻译过</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62RXaveygH5vBvphtzFhWCAt6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">罗素</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">的《</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60Vu3AoSLgrRN/6cP9cxCUCNu5AOtWml363pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrI8pbaiVjsTaVac5zdSSrIf5CPB8ohaihq4Zzuj7vhkMHh5d4ADz2oEw1pzeVCBaOexK80u/B26+VWZhAVR4xoKDA8Zu4mdgY0" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">西方哲学</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">史》他的学问功底扎实，没有任何水分。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=ce319c69afc379317d688621dbc5b784/f3ea15ce36d3d53900c151ac3a87e950342ab0e5.jpg" border="0" width="294" height="450" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">这本书年过50岁后的作家</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw63cRL388SYLx2xYYqozXmhbImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">史铁生</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">在患病期间对生命，人生，爱，和真善美的思考与感悟。观点深邃，文字灵透，很优秀，很感人的一本书</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=2515fa7c97dda144da096cba82b6d009/f9cec3fdfc039245ff4abf608794a4c27c1e25e5.jpg" border="0" width="312" height="426" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">这本书上下册，可以分开买，上册是17世纪以前的</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60Vu3AoSLgrRN/6cP9cxCUCNu5AOtWml363pfKJtUWCTh9ssyDK1SDlnhDg47fRGLxIC1WNLHU2MljwrjhG0RrI8pbaiVjsTaVac5zdSSrIf5CPB8ohaihq4Zzuj7vhkMHh5d4ADz2oEw1pzeVCBaOexK80u/B26+VWZhAVR4xoKDA8Zu4mdgY0" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">西方哲学</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">原著精选，编者把</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60yuAo0o//nw8fmfxscM4tnVGnxpav6gYwiY65SX2hsh16xSq+FxHP6FdK7DP1v3oStqBaZnWN6vVdC7Gg5eFCxxXwoI+JJTwYJ9jRveAcrmKRPfOLAL3uMNlSoYO4dfqlVC/wFR8Zk/s1ZVH6+BbfaQWGflJQWdFhd1HXE9UIilXY9qHh6BM0y" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">亚里士多德</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw600zzaaVhIB7v+GzxSByQY7ImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">伏尔泰</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62N/0yLVMGDfntI9+RzmdODt6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">卢梭</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw60FR/Owl9AR8qPrUXd7wvOoImOuUl9obIdesUqvhcRz+hXSuwz9b96EragWmZ1jer1XQuxoOXhQscV8KCPiSU8GCfY0b3gHK5ikT3ziwC97jDZUqGDuHX6pVQv8BUfGZP7NWVR+vgW32kFhn5SUFnRYXdR1xPVCIpV2Pah4egTNMg==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">笛卡尔</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">，</span><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62olM4knCqKmebk2JeEflfht6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">休谟</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">等人书中的观点经过专业的精挑细选后 既去掉了最艰深难懂的部分，又把他们最重要最清晰的观点展现了出来，值得一读。</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=86cc10b354e736d158138c00ab514ffc/9118972bd40735fad80f10d69e510fb30e2408e5.jpg" border="0" width="404" height="584" /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">以下这2本是公认的经典，没有长篇大论，对话录平易近人，但在普普通通的交流中，又透出了哲学的博大精深</span><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=f1bdf57007082838680ddc1c8898a964/14dda3cc7cd98d10d72b525e213fb80e7aec90e6.jpg" border="0" width="300" height="441" /><br /><a style="box-sizing: content-box; color: #2d64b3; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" href="http://jump.bdimg.com/safecheck/index?url=rN3wPs8te/pL4AOY0zAwhz3wi8AXlR5gsMEbyYdIw62CuaOXZAbtAxlKJXEQfBz8t6XyibVFgk4fbLMgytUg5Z4Q4OO30Ri8SAtVjSx1NjJY8K44RtEayPKW2olY7E2lWnOc3UkqyH+QjwfKIWooauGc7o+74ZDB4eXeAA89qBMNac3lQgWjnsSvNLvwduvlVmYQFUeMaCgwPGbuJnYGNA==" target="_blank" class="ps_cb">尼采</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333">更像是一位悲观主义气质浓烈的诗人，他的书总是充满了愤世嫉俗的警句格言，没有冗长的论证和繁琐的注释。全是短篇的言辞很洗练拔俗的独到见解。看过这书的好几个版本，包括有人推崇的鲁迅翻译版，但是发觉虽然鲁迅那时代翻译水准是很高的，但那种翻译文风明显和今天的时代语境是不相容的，所以读着，读着总会觉得有种小小的不适应，个人还是喜欢三联书店的这个版本，这应该是目前最好的版本。</span><br /><br /><br /><img style="box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 570px; cursor: url('http://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/static-pb/img/cur_zin.cur'); color: #333333; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px" class="BDE_Image" src="http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=718090adb2119313c743ffb855390c10/eb00baa1cd11728b65d3d24dc8fcc3cec2fd2ce6.jpg" border="0" width="200" height="293" />
